rows.label: fev01_110_151_msg0001
rows.name:
As expected, it's completely different
from sleeping in the hut
on Gramps' back...

rows.label: fev01_110_151_msg0002
rows.name:
For some reason, I feel like
I've gotten a bit stronger...

rows.label: fev01_110_151_msg0003
rows.name:
I should probably get going
to the rendezvous point now.

rows.label: fev01_110_151_msg0004
rows.name:
It was at Goldmund Exit Dock
down on the ground floor, right?

rows.label: fev01_110_151_msg0005
rows.name:
I suppose I could still wander
around Goldmund or do some
more shopping, but...

rows.label: fev01_110_151_msg0006
rows.name: In any case, time to get moving!
